<PageLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about Blog Worms – a UK-based content platform covering trending topics, viral stories, and unanswered questions from across Britain."
  breadcrumbLabel="About Us"
>
  <p class="text-lg text-surface-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
    Welcome to <strong>Blog Worms</strong> — a UK-based content platform dedicated to bringing you the most relevant, timely, and well-researched articles on topics that matter.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>
    Blog Worms was born out of a simple frustration: too many trending topics and frequently asked questions lacked proper, well-written answers. We noticed that when people across the UK searched for the latest trending story or tried to find answers to specific questions, they were often met with thin, unhelpful content that left them more confused than when they started.
  </p>
  <p>
    We decided to change that. Blog Worms was created to be the antidote to low-quality content — a place where every article is thoroughly researched, clearly written, and genuinely useful. Whether it's a breaking news story that's dominating Google Trends or an obscure question that nobody has properly answered, we dig in and deliver the content our readers deserve.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>
    Our mission is straightforward: <strong>to create the best possible content for the topics people are actually searching for</strong>. We monitor UK Google Trends, social media conversations, and search data to identify what's trending and what questions remain unanswered. Then we put in the work to create comprehensive, engaging articles that truly serve our readers.
  </p>

  <h2>What We Cover</h2>
  <p>Blog Worms focuses on three main content pillars:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Trending Topics</strong> — The hottest stories and topics breaking across the UK, from celebrity news to tech launches to cultural moments. We cover what's buzzing right now.</li>
    <li><strong>In-Depth Guides</strong> — Comprehensive how-to guides, explainers, and deep dives into subjects that need more than a quick answer. We take the time to do the research so you don't have to.</li>
    <li><strong>Unanswered Questions</strong> — The questions people are asking that Google hasn't properly answered yet. We find the gaps in online knowledge and fill them with quality content.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Accuracy</strong> — We fact-check our content and cite sources wherever possible. Trust is earned through accuracy.</li>
    <li><strong>Clarity</strong> — No jargon, no corporate speak. We write in plain English that respects your time and intelligence.</li>
    <li><strong>Timeliness</strong> — When something trends, we move quickly. Our readers expect fresh content, and we deliver.</li>
    <li><strong>Depth</strong> — We don't do surface-level. Every article aims to be the most comprehensive resource on its topic.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Team</h2>
  <p>
    Blog Worms is run by a small, dedicated team of writers and researchers based in the United Kingdom. We're passionate about great content and obsessed with understanding what people are searching for. Our team combines journalism experience, SEO expertise, and genuine curiosity to create content that ranks and reads well.
  </p>

  <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>
    We love hearing from our readers. Whether you have a topic suggestion, feedback on an article, or just want to say hello, don't hesitate to reach out through our <a href="/contact-us/">Contact Us</a> page. Every message is read by a real person on our team.
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you for reading Blog Worms. We're glad you're here.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
